lass=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tema-pesni/strannye-chuvstva&quot;&gt;Странные чувства&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tema-pesni/ya-s-toboy&quot;&gt;Я с тобой&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-chuvstva field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Чувства:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/dezhavyu&quot;&gt;Дежавю&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/lyubov&quot;&gt;Любовь&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/nablyudenie&quot;&gt;Наблюдение&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/skorb&quot;&gt;Скорбь&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/sozercanie&quot;&gt;Созерцание&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/sostradanie&quot;&gt;Сострадание&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/tyazhest&quot;&gt;Тяжесть&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/umirotvorenie&quot;&gt;Умиротворение&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/unynie&quot;&gt;Уныние&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/chuvstvo/frustraciya&quot;&gt;Фрустрация&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
